1341::$$$message_0011_0000_0000$$$::I suppose...[lr]::
1342::$$$message_0011_0000_0001$$$::I should take a little break before my evening training.::
1343::$$$message_0011_0001_0000$$$::"The bath's been filled, and I guess I can ask Fuji-nee to take Sakura home."[lr]::
1344::$$$message_0011_0001_0001$$$::Now that's settled, I should be as efficient as I can.[lr]::
1345::$$$message_0011_0001_0002$$$::First I need to wake Fuji-nee up, since she's dozing in the living room. Then I'll thank Sakura for dinner and see the two of them off on their way home. Then I'll take a bath and rest a bit more.::

